  <h2>Documentation Structure</h2>
  <p>The documentation is organized as follows:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Getting Started</strong>: Introduction, installation, and quickstart guides</li>
    <li><strong>Core Concepts</strong>: Information about the Compound protocol and supported networks/markets</li>
    <li><strong>Hooks</strong>: Documentation for all the hooks provided by the library</li>
    <li><strong>API Reference</strong>: Detailed API reference for the library</li>
    <li><strong>Examples</strong>: Example code snippets and use cases</li>
  </ul>

